    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.幫助學生熟悉英文閱讀技巧，例如根據上下文判斷字義。<br>2.培養獨立閱讀英文文章之能力，例如如何掌握文章大意。<br>3.閱讀不同類型的文章，強化學生辨識文章組織結構之能力。<br>4.使學生熟悉英文寫作不同文體的寫作策略。<br>",
        "en": "1.To familiarize students with English reading skills, such as getting meanings of the words from context<br>2.To develop students’ abilities to read English texts independently, such as understanding the main idea<br>3.To help students read different types of texts and to enhance their abilities of identifying the text structure<br>4.To familiarize students with writing strategies of different genres<br>"
